1
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:08,800
Jinwang.

2
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,600
Master.

3
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,660
Brother Qingxuan.

4
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,200
Hahaha.

5
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,480
I underestimated you.

6
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,440
You really descended to the mortal realm and became a demon.

7
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,880
Not exactly a demon,

8
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,100
just seeking freedom.

9
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:00,960
Master,

10
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,520
you know each other?

11
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,880
I didn't expect

12
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,200
you to fall this low.

13
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,160
Fall?

14
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,880
High Immortal,

15
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,560
have you not fallen as well?

16
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,279
Back then,

17
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,360
I looked up to you so much.

18
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:24,100
My descent to the mortal realm

19
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,880
is the will of Heaven.

20
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,360
Then my descent

21
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,500
is to break the will of Heaven.

22
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,840
You don't think

23
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:37,250
that by severing my immortal root,

24
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,240
you can defeat me, do you?

25
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,960
I'm not that overconfident.

26
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,159
But

27
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,570
to take you away,

28
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,080
I have many other ways.

29
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,159
Master, save me!

30
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,440
Master!

31
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,800
Let the child go.

32
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,170
I'll go with you.

33
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:21,410
Don't treat me like a three-year-old.

34
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,340
If you want to save your disciple,

35
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,680
we'll meet at Tushan.

36
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,240
Ancestor!

37
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:41,240
That demoness had it planned all along.

38
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,610
I didn't catch them.

39
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,560
They got away.

40
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,420
Save the people first.

41
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:35,200
A single thought of gods and buddhas saves all beings.

42
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:38,840
A single thought of demonic obsession throws the universe into chaos.

43
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,240
Save others and yourself with compassion.

44
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,200
When you comprehend the true path of your heart again,

45
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,280
you may return to the immortal path

46
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,420
and ascend the cloud steps once more.

47
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,320
Brother Qingxuan,

48
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,050
when are we going to save Feilu?

49
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,400
When did I say I was going to save him?

50
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,440
What did you say?

51
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,100
Since those demons have left,

52
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,760
I assume they won't return.

53
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:26,600
The officials from the Sitian Bureau

54
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,400
should also be on their way here.

55
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,420
My entanglement with Ercheng ends here.

56
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,159
As soon as day breaks,

57
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,409
I will take my leave.

58
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,800
Immortal, you've saved Ercheng many times.

59
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,760
It's not too late to leave after we present you with a small gift.

60
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:39,159
Yes.

61
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:39,840
No need.

62
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,440
I've been a bit tired lately.

63
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,800
Prepare a horse for me.

64
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,600
But...

65
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,000
Just do as I say.

66
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,560
And you,

67
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,880
don't follow me anymore.

68
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,480
Hey!

69
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,480
You don't care about Feilu anymore?

70
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,040
He was taken because of you.

71
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,010
My immortal body has been severed,

72
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,480
my form is broken.

73
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,210
Even if I go to Tushan in person,

74
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,960
it would be a waste of effort.

75
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,200
In this world,

76
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,930
I still have unfinished business.

77
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,090
As for Feilu,

78
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,480
he will have to rely on his own destiny.

79
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,120
You!

80
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:22,880
Feilu also calls you Master.

81
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,660
I never said I would accept him as a disciple.

82
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,060
Just like Hu San calling me Ancestor,

83
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,130
it's just wishful thinking on their part.

84
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:34,640
As for you,

85
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,280
you're just a tree demon.

86
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,559
If I wanted to subdue you,

87
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,370
you wouldn't last three moves.

88
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:45,340
Considering you've helped the people along the way

89
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,320
and haven't done any more evil deeds,

90
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,840
I'll spare you for now.

91
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,160
If you bother me again,

92
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,160
I will not spare you.

93
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,200
What Golden Immortal?

94
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:07,700
You're just a coward who clings to life and fears death!

95
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,200
Immortal, you saved Ercheng.

96
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,760
We are deeply grateful

97
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,040
and have come to see you off.

98
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,760
However, most of the people are still healing.

99
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,160
They cannot come to see you off.

100
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,640
Please do not be offended.

101
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,560
Please accept our bow.

102
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,560
The seven human emotions

103
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,300
cause all kinds of suffering,

104
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,680
which are hard to control.

105
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:42,210
I hope you will behave yourselves from now on.

106
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,060
Do not make any more mistakes.

107
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,480
Yes, yes.

108
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,280
Thank you, Immortal. Thank you.

109
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,240
The bearing of an immortal

110
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,880
is indeed extraordinary.

111
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,210
County Magistrate,

112
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,120
why don't we submit a petition

113
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:11,080
to change the name of Ercheng to Xuancheng?

114
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,600
What do you think?

115
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,560
Excellent.

116
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,890
Absolutely excellent.

117
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,340
What are you doing?

118
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,080
I saved a lot of people.

119
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,330
Have you ever seen him ride a horse before?

120
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,200
No.

121
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,300
He's always traveled on foot.

122
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,970
I thought Golden Immortals could fly.

123
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,560
That's called riding the wind.

124
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,760
What do you mean, fly?

125
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,480
Wait a minute.

126
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,970
He's never even ridden a horse before.

127
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,280
Don't you think that's strange?

128
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,090
Didn't he say he was a bit tired?

129
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,680
With his powers,

130
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,100
even if his immortal roots were severed,

131
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,360
he never had the habit of riding horses.

132
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,280
The martial world is so big.

133
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:23,680
He could just walk and travel slowly.

134
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,240
When things are out of the ordinary,

135
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,720
there must be something fishy going on.

136
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,200
I noticed that you

137
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,120
are prejudiced against demons.

138
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,280
Look at the direction he's heading.

139
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,400
It's toward Tushan.

140
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,400
He's going to save Feilu.

141
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,730
Tushan is where the demons of the Tushan clan gather.

142
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:46,600
He must be afraid of implicating us,

143
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,200
so he decided to go alone.

144
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,040
I'm leaving.

145
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,480
Where are you going?

146
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,280
To save Feilu.

147
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,130
Why are you still following me?

148
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,840
Ping Jie Qiang Hai Hui.

149
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,000
Jie Qiang Hai.
